<body region="r1">
<div>
<p begin="00:00:03.760" end="00:00:07.839" style="s2">All right,</p>
<p begin="00:00:05.359" end="00:00:09.679" style="s2">I want to welcome everybody to night</p>
<p begin="00:00:07.839" end="00:00:11.360" style="s2">school. We have a bunch of people</p>
<p begin="00:00:09.679" end="00:00:14.240" style="s2">popping in, so we&#39;re going to give them</p>
<p begin="00:00:11.360" end="00:00:17.199" style="s2">a few minutes.</p>
<p begin="00:00:14.240" end="00:00:20.000" style="s2">And as everybody pops in here in the</p>
<p begin="00:00:17.199" end="00:00:22.160" style="s2">chat, let&#39;s write wherever we&#39;re coming</p>
<p begin="00:00:20.000" end="00:00:26.000" style="s2">in from. So, is it New York? You&#39;re in</p>
<p begin="00:00:22.160" end="00:00:30.519" style="s2">Austin, Texas, SF, around the world. Let</p>
<p begin="00:00:26.000" end="00:00:30.519" style="s2">us know where you&#39;re dialing in from.</p>
<p begin="00:00:31.439" end="00:00:35.600" style="s2">Now, we have over 400 people signed up</p>
<p begin="00:00:33.680" end="00:00:37.680" style="s2">for this session. So, there&#39;s going to</p>
<p begin="00:00:35.600" end="00:00:40.239" style="s2">be a lot of people all over the place.</p>
<p begin="00:00:37.680" end="00:00:42.800" style="s2">So, I&#39;m excited to see Louisiana, New</p>
<p begin="00:00:40.239" end="00:00:46.320" style="s2">Zealand. That&#39;s the farthest.</p>
<p begin="00:00:42.800" end="00:00:48.640" style="s2">We have Orange County, Canada.</p>
<p begin="00:00:46.320" end="00:00:51.200" style="s2">Love it.</p>
<p begin="00:00:48.640" end="00:00:53.360" style="s2">Now, there&#39;s a few people in the room</p>
<p begin="00:00:51.200" end="00:00:56.239" style="s2">who are going to be sort of my helpers,</p>
<p begin="00:00:53.360" end="00:00:57.680" style="s2">staff members from Gauntlet. you&#39;ll see</p>
<p begin="00:00:56.239" end="00:01:00.239" style="s2">uh they&#39;re going to write with Gauntlet</p>
<p begin="00:00:57.680" end="00:01:02.399" style="s2">or from Gauntlet on their display names.</p>
<p begin="00:01:00.239" end="00:01:04.640" style="s2">So, help answer some of your questions.</p>
<p begin="00:01:02.399" end="00:01:07.760" style="s2">But as you&#39;re hopping into this class,</p>
<p begin="00:01:04.640" end="00:01:09.920" style="s2">please add where you&#39;re dialing in from.</p>
<p begin="00:01:07.760" end="00:01:11.760" style="s2">And let&#39;s also add why we are joining</p>
<p begin="00:01:09.920" end="00:01:13.760" style="s2">this class.</p>
<p begin="00:01:11.760" end="00:01:16.479" style="s2">Why are you joining this class on how to</p>
<p begin="00:01:13.760" end="00:01:19.200" style="s2">interview as an AI first engineer? I</p>
<p begin="00:01:16.479" end="00:01:20.960" style="s2">want to deliver value to you guys. And</p>
<p begin="00:01:19.200" end="00:01:23.759" style="s2">so, this is completely live. I&#39;ll be</p>
<p begin="00:01:20.960" end="00:01:28.200" style="s2">doing a ton of Q&amp;A at the end. So, what</p>
<p begin="00:01:23.759" end="00:01:28.200" style="s2">is the reason why you joined the class?</p>
<p begin="00:01:31.360" end="00:01:35.560" style="s2">Poland. That&#39;s another one.</p>
<p begin="00:01:36.960" end="00:01:42.640" style="s2">New Hampshire. All right.</p>
<p begin="00:01:40.640" end="00:01:44.960" style="s2">Okay. You don&#39;t interview well. Looking</p>
<p begin="00:01:42.640" end="00:01:47.280" style="s2">for a better job to get better</p>
<p begin="00:01:44.960" end="00:01:50.560" style="s2">understanding.</p>
<p begin="00:01:47.280" end="00:01:52.640" style="s2">transitioning from senior writer former</p>
<p begin="00:01:50.560" end="00:01:54.720" style="s2">Lambda school.</p>
<p begin="00:01:52.640" end="00:01:57.920" style="s2">Yes, the session is going to be recorded</p>
<p begin="00:01:54.720" end="00:01:59.680" style="s2">and available on YouTube afterward.</p>
<p begin="00:01:57.920" end="00:02:02.799" style="s2">I have an opportunity to join an AI</p>
<p begin="00:01:59.680" end="00:02:05.280" style="s2">company. Amazing. McKini, Texas, looking</p>
<p begin="00:02:02.799" end="00:02:08.080" style="s2">for a job.</p>
<p begin="00:02:05.280" end="00:02:13.399" style="s2">Transitioning from TPM to AI engineer.</p>
<p begin="00:02:08.080" end="00:02:13.399" style="s2">Love it. Exploring the AI landscape.</p>
<p begin="00:02:13.440" end="00:02:17.239" style="s2">Looking for a better job.</p>
<p begin="00:02:17.760" end="00:02:21.680" style="s2">would love to learn more about</p>
<p begin="00:02:19.280" end="00:02:25.360" style="s2">experimenting. Don&#39;t interview well.</p>
<p begin="00:02:21.680" end="00:02:27.440" style="s2">Imposter syndrome, of course.</p>
<p begin="00:02:25.360" end="00:02:30.239" style="s2">This is great. The awesome part about</p>
<p begin="00:02:27.440" end="00:02:32.160" style="s2">this is</p>
<p begin="00:02:30.239" end="00:02:34.160" style="s2">this is going to help me decide what</p>
<p begin="00:02:32.160" end="00:02:36.400" style="s2">other classes I should have for night</p>
<p begin="00:02:34.160" end="00:02:38.560" style="s2">school. So the whole point of night</p>
<p begin="00:02:36.400" end="00:02:41.200" style="s2">scroll is to take the gauntlet AI</p>
<p begin="00:02:38.560" end="00:02:43.440" style="s2">curriculum and to ensure that there is</p>
<p begin="00:02:41.200" end="00:02:46.000" style="s2">an open version of that curriculum that</p>
<p begin="00:02:43.440" end="00:02:48.000" style="s2">all of you can use to get better at</p>
<p begin="00:02:46.000" end="00:02:50.160" style="s2">either a technical skill, an</p>
<p begin="00:02:48.000" end="00:02:52.720" style="s2">interviewing skill, and just get hired</p>
<p begin="00:02:50.160" end="00:02:55.440" style="s2">much faster in this job market. So I&#39;m</p>
<p begin="00:02:52.720" end="00:02:56.800" style="s2">excited to see all this inside of the</p>
<p begin="00:02:55.440" end="00:02:59.280" style="s2">chat so we can actually see what the</p>
<p begin="00:02:56.800" end="00:03:01.760" style="s2">next classes might be. We&#39;re going to</p>
<p begin="00:02:59.280" end="00:03:03.680" style="s2">give people another minute. We have 109</p>
<p begin="00:03:01.760" end="00:03:06.400" style="s2">people already joining us. We&#39;re going</p>
<p begin="00:03:03.680" end="00:03:08.319" style="s2">to get started here in just a minute and</p>
<p begin="00:03:06.400" end="00:03:12.400" style="s2">we&#39;ll get started on our session on how</p>
<p begin="00:03:08.319" end="00:03:13.920" style="s2">to interview as an AI first engineer.</p>
<p begin="00:03:12.400" end="00:03:15.519" style="s2">Someone is saying being an AI engineer</p>
<p begin="00:03:13.920" end="00:03:18.080" style="s2">is a completely new role to me and it&#39;s</p>
<p begin="00:03:15.519" end="00:03:21.200" style="s2">an interesting change for sure. This is</p>
<p begin="00:03:18.080" end="00:03:24.879" style="s2">a role that didn&#39;t exist 8 months ago,</p>
<p begin="00:03:21.200" end="00:03:26.400" style="s2">right? The 8 months ago this role was</p>
<p begin="00:03:24.879" end="00:03:28.959" style="s2">completely something that people were</p>
<p begin="00:03:26.400" end="00:03:31.920" style="s2">thinking about. HR didn&#39;t have a name</p>
<p begin="00:03:28.959" end="00:03:34.640" style="s2">for it. All of a sudden, cloud code</p>
<p begin="00:03:31.920" end="00:03:37.120" style="s2">reaches a maxima and everybody is</p>
<p begin="00:03:34.640" end="00:03:38.400" style="s2">looking for an AI first engineer. And so</p>
<p begin="00:03:37.120" end="00:03:40.239" style="s2">I think this is going to be really</p>
<p begin="00:03:38.400" end="00:03:42.640" style="s2">insightful for all of you and I&#39;m</p>
<p begin="00:03:40.239" end="00:03:44.560" style="s2">excited to get started. Okay, so I want</p>
<p begin="00:03:42.640" end="00:03:46.799" style="s2">to go through how night school works.</p>
<p begin="00:03:44.560" end="00:03:49.120" style="s2">Night School is a weekly session that we</p>
<p begin="00:03:46.799" end="00:03:51.280" style="s2">have here at Gauntlet AI that is open to</p>
<p begin="00:03:49.120" end="00:03:54.480" style="s2">the public. And this session is going to</p>
<p begin="00:03:51.280" end="00:03:57.040" style="s2">go over either a technical skill, a soft</p>
<p begin="00:03:54.480" end="00:03:58.879" style="s2">skill, or something that has to do with</p>
<p begin="00:03:57.040" end="00:04:01.840" style="s2">both of those areas when it comes to</p>
<p begin="00:03:58.879" end="00:04:05.360" style="s2">getting hired as an AI engineer. We run</p>
<p begin="00:04:01.840" end="00:04:07.840" style="s2">a 10-week accelerator, 3 weeks remote, 7</p>
<p begin="00:04:05.360" end="00:04:10.640" style="s2">weeks on-site, where all we do is</p>
<p begin="00:04:07.840" end="00:04:12.640" style="s2">completely immerse ourselves in AI. That</p>
<p begin="00:04:10.640" end="00:04:14.319" style="s2">means I have over a hundred students at</p>
<p begin="00:04:12.640" end="00:04:17.120" style="s2">our headquarters right now in Austin,</p>
<p begin="00:04:14.319" end="00:04:20.320" style="s2">Texas that are devoting over a thousand</p>
<p begin="00:04:17.120" end="00:04:22.479" style="s2">hours to being at the frontier of AI. My</p>
<p begin="00:04:20.320" end="00:04:24.479" style="s2">goal is to take that curriculum and</p>
<p begin="00:04:22.479" end="00:04:27.520" style="s2">bring it to you for free. So, if you</p>
<p begin="00:04:24.479" end="00:04:29.520" style="s2">have questions, if you have uh specific</p>
<p begin="00:04:27.520" end="00:04:31.440" style="s2">concerns, if you&#39;re wondering about</p>
<p begin="00:04:29.520" end="00:04:34.080" style="s2">something, please, please, please add it</p>
<p begin="00:04:31.440" end="00:04:36.960" style="s2">to the chat. Here&#39;s how Q&amp;A is going to</p>
<p begin="00:04:34.080" end="00:04:39.680" style="s2">work. I have three of my Gauntlet staff</p>
<p begin="00:04:36.960" end="00:04:41.360" style="s2">members, Derek, Aaron, and Nina, inside</p>
<p begin="00:04:39.680" end="00:04:43.120" style="s2">of the chat with you. They&#39;re going to</p>
<p begin="00:04:41.360" end="00:04:45.840" style="s2">be able to answer your questions on the</p>
<p begin="00:04:43.120" end="00:04:48.320" style="s2">fly as I&#39;m teaching. At the end of my</p>
<p begin="00:04:45.840" end="00:04:51.680" style="s2">session, I&#39;ll be spending about 15 to 30</p>
<p begin="00:04:48.320" end="00:04:54.080" style="s2">minutes on Q&amp;A alone. I&#39;ve also asked</p>
<p begin="00:04:51.680" end="00:04:56.720" style="s2">the staff, Sunny and Tom, to highlight</p>
<p begin="00:04:54.080" end="00:04:58.000" style="s2">some of the best questions for me. These</p>
<p begin="00:04:56.720" end="00:05:00.400" style="s2">best questions are then being</p>
<p begin="00:04:58.000" end="00:05:03.120" style="s2">highlighted on my phone here, so I can</p>
<p begin="00:05:00.400" end="00:05:04.880" style="s2">actually answer them out loud. So, we&#39;re</p>
<p begin="00:05:03.120" end="00:05:06.160" style="s2">there&#39;s a lot of people in the room, so</p>
<p begin="00:05:04.880" end="00:05:08.240" style="s2">we&#39;re going to do our best to make sure</p>
<p begin="00:05:06.160" end="00:05:10.320" style="s2">all your questions are answered. But</p>
<p begin="00:05:08.240" end="00:05:12.960" style="s2">here&#39;s what you should do for the next</p>
<p begin="00:05:10.320" end="00:05:15.120" style="s2">40 to 45 minutes. Lock in, pay attention</p>
<p begin="00:05:12.960" end="00:05:17.440" style="s2">to what I&#39;m trying to say, participate</p>
<p begin="00:05:15.120" end="00:05:19.919" style="s2">in some of the exercises, note down your</p>
<p begin="00:05:17.440" end="00:05:22.160" style="s2">question in the chat, and we&#39;ll have one</p>
<p begin="00:05:19.919" end="00:05:24.080" style="s2">of our staff members answer it async or</p>
<p begin="00:05:22.160" end="00:05:26.560" style="s2">I&#39;ll answer it out loud at the end of</p>
<p begin="00:05:24.080" end="00:05:28.720" style="s2">the session. This is exactly how classes</p>
<p begin="00:05:26.560" end="00:05:31.199" style="s2">work here at Gauntlet AI. We take a</p>
<p begin="00:05:28.720" end="00:05:33.520" style="s2">portion of the class and have it focused</p>
<p begin="00:05:31.199" end="00:05:35.600" style="s2">on the lecture material. Once the</p>
<p begin="00:05:33.520" end="00:05:38.080" style="s2">lecture material is over, we usually</p>
<p begin="00:05:35.600" end="00:05:40.639" style="s2">have a Q&amp;A session for about 15 to 30</p>
<p begin="00:05:38.080" end="00:05:42.800" style="s2">minutes and then an exercise at the end</p>
<p begin="00:05:40.639" end="00:05:44.479" style="s2">that individuals can do to sort of get</p>
<p begin="00:05:42.800" end="00:05:46.240" style="s2">prepared and take themselves to the next</p>
<p begin="00:05:44.479" end="00:05:48.479" style="s2">level. That&#39;s exactly what we&#39;ll be</p>
<p begin="00:05:46.240" end="00:05:51.479" style="s2">doing today.</p>
<p begin="00:05:48.479" end="00:05:51.479" style="s2">All right.</p>
<p begin="00:05:52.240" end="00:05:57.759" style="s2">Today&#39;s class is going to be on how to</p>
<p begin="00:05:54.639" end="00:05:59.759" style="s2">interview as an AI first engineer. The</p>
<p begin="00:05:57.759" end="00:06:01.840" style="s2">reason why I think I can talk about this</p>
<p begin="00:05:59.759" end="00:06:04.000" style="s2">is because I&#39;ve partnered with over 81</p>
<p begin="00:06:01.840" end="00:06:05.520" style="s2">companies and teams. I&#39;ve trained over a</p>
<p begin="00:06:04.000" end="00:06:07.919" style="s2">thousand engineers over the last two</p>
<p begin="00:06:05.520" end="00:06:11.280" style="s2">years and I&#39;ve placed over 300 gauntlet</p>
<p begin="00:06:07.919" end="00:06:13.680" style="s2">grads as AI first engineers. We partner</p>
<p begin="00:06:11.280" end="00:06:17.280" style="s2">with organizations like</p>
<p begin="00:06:13.680" end="00:06:19.199" style="s2">GoFundMe, Zapier, Nerdy, Nexa, and my</p>
<p begin="00:06:17.280" end="00:06:21.440" style="s2">graduates are becoming AI first</p>
<p begin="00:06:19.199" end="00:06:24.000" style="s2">engineers at all of these organizations.</p>
<p begin="00:06:21.440" end="00:06:26.080" style="s2">Our goal here at Gauntlet is to train</p>
<p begin="00:06:24.000" end="00:06:28.560" style="s2">the next generation of engineers,</p>
<p begin="00:06:26.080" end="00:06:31.520" style="s2">leaders, managers, and business owners</p>
<p begin="00:06:28.560" end="00:06:34.080" style="s2">to be AI first across the board. That is</p>
<p begin="00:06:31.520" end="00:06:36.720" style="s2">why I can come to you and say I</p>
<p begin="00:06:34.080" end="00:06:39.440" style="s2">understand how people are trying to hire</p>
<p begin="00:06:36.720" end="00:06:41.840" style="s2">for these AI roles. I&#39;ve talked to CTO&#39;s</p>
<p begin="00:06:39.440" end="00:06:45.280" style="s2">across the board. I&#39;ve hired personally</p>
<p begin="00:06:41.840" end="00:06:48.560" style="s2">as a CTO and the system is entirely</p>
<p begin="00:06:45.280" end="00:06:53.039" style="s2">broken. This is real data from a job</p>
<p begin="00:06:48.560" end="00:06:57.039" style="s2">posting that I recently had where 88% of</p>
<p begin="00:06:53.039" end="00:07:00.319" style="s2">all of the applications I got were AI</p>
<p begin="00:06:57.039" end="00:07:03.120" style="s2">generated resumes. You could tell by how</p>
<p begin="00:07:00.319" end="00:07:05.440" style="s2">exact the keywords were being used. You</p>
<p begin="00:07:03.120" end="00:07:08.160" style="s2">could tell by how precise everything</p>
<p begin="00:07:05.440" end="00:07:10.240" style="s2">matched my job description. You can tell</p>
<p begin="00:07:08.160" end="00:07:13.680" style="s2">that it&#39;s just really hard to find</p>
<p begin="00:07:10.240" end="00:07:15.199" style="s2">signal in a sea of noise. There is so</p>
<p begin="00:07:13.680" end="00:07:17.840" style="s2">much noise out there where people are</p>
<p begin="00:07:15.199" end="00:07:19.599" style="s2">claiming overexaggerating and not</p>
<p begin="00:07:17.840" end="00:07:22.319" style="s2">actually talking to the exact skill set</p>
<p begin="00:07:19.599" end="00:07:23.919" style="s2">that they have. When you actually start</p>
<p begin="00:07:22.319" end="00:07:26.240" style="s2">talking to these people and you start</p>
<p begin="00:07:23.919" end="00:07:28.000" style="s2">interviewing them, you realize, hey, he</p>
<p begin="00:07:26.240" end="00:07:30.800" style="s2">doesn&#39;t actually have the knowledge for</p>
<p begin="00:07:28.000" end="00:07:32.720" style="s2">this specific position or no, they did</p>
<p begin="00:07:30.800" end="00:07:34.960" style="s2">something similar, but it&#39;s not exactly</p>
<p begin="00:07:32.720" end="00:07:37.680" style="s2">what I&#39;m looking for. Based on that job</p>
<p begin="00:07:34.960" end="00:07:40.880" style="s2">posting, I had 88% which I thought were</p>
<p begin="00:07:37.680" end="00:07:43.680" style="s2">AI generated résumés. I saw identical</p>
<p begin="00:07:40.880" end="00:07:46.880" style="s2">keywords for about 76% of that uh those</p>
<p begin="00:07:43.680" end="00:07:48.400" style="s2">applications. About 12% in my opinion</p>
<p begin="00:07:46.880" end="00:07:51.360" style="s2">were like, &quot;Okay, this guy&#39;s probably</p>
<p begin="00:07:48.400" end="00:07:53.919" style="s2">good. He has a brand name. He has a</p>
<p begin="00:07:51.360" end="00:07:55.680" style="s2">referral. There&#39;s some signal here that</p>
<p begin="00:07:53.919" end="00:07:57.520" style="s2">makes it me seem like, hey, this is</p>
<p begin="00:07:55.680" end="00:07:59.840" style="s2">actually a valid candidate.&quot; And then</p>
<p begin="00:07:57.520" end="00:08:02.400" style="s2">finally, about 8% did move on to the</p>
